PluginEnricherInput.expression: CONCAT_WS(',', AddressLine1, AddressLine2, City, StateProvince, Country, LEFT(Zipcode, 5))

SemQLMatchRule.condition: SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.EnrichedAddressLine1, Record2.EnrichedAddressLine1) > 70 and SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.EnrichedAddressLine2, Record2.EnrichedAddressLine2) > 70 and Record1.EnrichedCity = Record2.EnrichedCity and Record1.EnrichedCounty = Record1.EnrichedCounty
SemQLMatchRule.label: Location Fuzzy Match
SemQLMatchRule.name: LocationFuzzyMatch

SemQLMatchRule.condition: SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.Customer.EnrichedFullName, Record2.Customer.EnrichedFullName) > 70 and SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.Location.EnrichedAddressLine1, Record2.Location.EnrichedAddressLine1) > 70 and SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.Location.EnrichedAddressLine1, Record2.Location.AddressLine2) > 70 and SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.Location.City, Record2.Location.City) > 70 and Record1.Location.StateProvince = Record2.Location.StateProvince
SemQLMatchRule.label: Address Fuzzy Match
SemQLMatchRule.name: AddressFuzzyMatch

SemQLMatchRule.condition: Record1.IdentifierName = Record2.IdentifierName and Record1.IdentifierValue = Record2.IdentifierValue and SEM_EDIT_DISTANCE_SIMILARITY(Record1.Customer.EnrichedFullName, Record2.Customer.EnrichedFullName) > 70
SemQLMatchRule.label: Identifier Exact Match
SemQLMatchRule.name: IdentifierExactMatch
